Interface MainMVFabric

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    AdminMVFabric, CacheMVFabric, ClientMVFabric
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AdminMVFabricImpl, CacheMVFabricImpl, ClientMVFabricImpl, MainMVFabricImpl

    public interface MainMVFabric
    The interface provides a set of standard methods for creates and returns the main modelAndViews.
